#. <section class="sutta" id="sn47.40"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn47.40:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 47"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 47"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn47.40:0.2"
msgid "4. Ananussutavagga"
msgstr "4. Not Learned From Anyone Else"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn47.40:0.3"
msgid "40. Vibhaṅgasutta"
msgstr "40. Analysis"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn47.40:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Satipaṭṭhānañca vo, bhikkhave, desessāmi satipaṭṭhānabhāvanañca "
"satipaṭṭhānabhāvanāgāminiñca paṭipadaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I will teach you mindfulness meditation, the development of "
"mindfulness meditation, and the practice that leads to the development of "
"mindfulness meditation."

msgctxt "sn47.40:1.2"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha."
msgstr "Listen …"

msgctxt "sn47.40:1.3"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, satipaṭṭhānaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is mindfulness meditation?"

msgctxt "sn47.40:1.4"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kāye kāyānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā, "
"vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant meditates by observing an aspect of the body—keen, "
"aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world."

msgctxt "sn47.40:1.5"
msgid "vedanāsu vedanānupassī viharati … pe …"
msgstr "They meditate observing an aspect of feelings …"

msgctxt "sn47.40:1.6"
msgid "citte cittānupassī viharati … pe …"
msgstr "mind …"

msgctxt "sn47.40:1.7"
msgid ""
"dhammesu dhammānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke "
"abhijjhādomanassaṃ."
msgstr ""
"principles—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the "
"world."

msgctxt "sn47.40:1.8"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, satipaṭṭhānaṃ."
msgstr "This is called mindfulness meditation."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn47.40:2.1"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, satipaṭṭhānabhāvanā?"
msgstr "And what is the development of mindfulness meditation?"

msgctxt "sn47.40:2.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu samudayadhammānupassī kāyasmiṃ viharati, "
"vayadhammānupassī kāyasmiṃ viharati, samudayavayadhammānupassī kāyasmiṃ "
"viharati, ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant meditates observing the body as liable to originate, "
"as liable to vanish, and as liable to originate and vanish—keen, aware, and "
"mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world."

msgctxt "sn47.40:2.3"
msgid "Samudayadhammānupassī vedanāsu viharati … pe …"
msgstr "They observe feelings …"

msgctxt "sn47.40:2.4"
msgid "samudayadhammānupassī citte viharati … pe …"
msgstr "mind …"

msgctxt "sn47.40:2.5"
msgid ""
"samudayadhammānupassī dhammesu viharati, vayadhammānupassī dhammesu "
"viharati, samudayavayadhammānupassī dhammesu viharati, ātāpī sampajāno "
"satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ."
msgstr ""
"principles as liable to originate, as liable to vanish, and as liable to "
"originate and vanish—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion "
"for the world."

msgctxt "sn47.40:2.6"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, satipaṭṭhānabhāvanā."
msgstr "This is called the development of mindfulness meditation."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn47.40:3.1"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, satipaṭṭhānabhāvanāgāminī paṭipadā?"
msgstr ""
"And what is the practice that leads to the development of mindfulness "
"meditation?"

msgctxt "sn47.40:3.2"
msgid "Ayameva ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr "It is simply this noble eightfold path, that is:"

msgctxt "sn47.40:3.3"
msgid ""
"sammādiṭṭhi, sammāsaṅkappo, sammāvācā, sammākammanto, sammāājīvo, "
"sammāvāyāmo, sammāsati, sammāsamādhi."
msgstr ""
"right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, "
"right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion."

msgctxt "sn47.40:3.4"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, satipaṭṭhānabhāvanāgāminī paṭipadā”ti."
msgstr ""
"This is called the practice that leads to the development of mindfulness "
"meditation.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn47.40:3.5"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn47.40:3.6"
msgid "Ananussutavaggo catuttho."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.184"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn47.40:4.1"
msgid "Ananussutaṃ virāgo,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn47.40:4.2"
msgid "viraddho bhāvanā sati;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn47.40:4.3"
msgid "Aññā chandaṃ pariññāya,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn47.40:4.4"
msgid "bhāvanā vibhaṅgena cāti."
msgstr ""
